            <div type="translation">
                <p>Truly blessed and thrice-blessed is the one who has gained self-control, humility, and love.</p> 
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The text derives from the Saint Ephraim the Syrian's homily "Sermo de virtutibus et vitiis", chapter 22, Περὶ ἐγκρατείας, incipit: Μακάριος ἀληθῶς καὶ τρισμακάριος ὁ ἐγκράτειαν φυλάξας. </p>
            </div>
